ats in Latin America. Everything you need to keep your Android safe, protected against malicious activities, andfree from virus, malware, or spyware.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Cleanup:</strong>&nbsp;removal of junk files that compromise the phone&#39;s performance. PSafe Total cleans your cache and temporary files, and even lets you delete pre-installed applications &ndash; freeing up internal memory and SD card space to fit new Apps, photos and videos.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Booster:</strong>&nbsp;Optimizes performance to make your Android faster. Speed up your mobile and free up RAM with just one click, througha convenient &ldquo;floating window&rdquo; on the home screen.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Vault:</strong>&nbsp;unbeatable app-lock protection to enhance the privacy of your personal information. Lock your applications, photos, SMS, calendar, orcontacts with a second password, even if the device itself is left unlocked.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Anti-theft:</strong>&nbsp;Locate,track and manage your device from anywhere through PSafe Total&rsquo;s convenient web interface. In case of loss or theft, you can block access and functions, wipe your data, and even disable<strong> <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\">the phone</a></strong>.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Other features:</strong>&nbsp;Verification (3-in-1: antivirus, booster and cleanup with just one touch); Total Apps (PSafe&rsquo;s showcase of other appoved, secure applications that won&rsquo;t infect your device); Backup (cloud copy of the device default settings, contacts, SMS and events, which can be easily imported or exported).</p>\n', 'PSafe Tecnologia S.A.', 'September 8, 2015', 125117, 'ON', 'none'),
(48, 'Samsung Milk Music Android', 'android', '15M', '1.5.1700012604', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.samsung.mdl.radio&hl=en', 'fsdgsdg.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/f4_DjujTTKobVHG9UtmT8DEHZjR6U_c1AEWS9Yx3cjloN_-CoIkgLTe75Xi5rt80WWo=h310-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/8p702QUzXyiFKFanVmoZiB6MGJYQLpDn3D9ymt9MXx1TUdzAjp0tPDloxh3nMyVrjA=h310-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/jl9UOoR2f8784rvqeDxdaejhnlKJih53KGE9R1Zi-cnH4oD9gcwgeedIqrtH6eHBtLda=h310-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/QMdwyoPv3V98P8hL9uKDlMGWPzF8PCrCL8exuY4SNHen9S6zoYJBA9qdewp70AHMLHKY=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/G3h7ezMZ6T3FOuG8oujelEczbWLk-d4qumsVjtL76b18SUJBqyJyBQNt6uXfseIA974=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/RkNyJmIZdPh75G2dRy9pe6TRfpykBazDEzEJqjE8hTKyazuT9BMIFRmy0ENh3fmrmxM=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/5C23nNhJSXav961KAREIu7691nK9k5ikRHcxJYLkI0ruUOhXJRazJ53Qy1uo87Evr4A=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/jUp3ktpF269fC3CieJkBE6ebAp3q2P-QtpEPRBN2OGxo6H3N17ohGkKK8fKSoIv_FnU=h900-rw\">[END_IMAGE]<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Samsung Milk Music?</strong></h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=48\"><strong>Samsung Milk Music</strong></a>&nbsp;is a free streaming radio service that offers a simple way to surface the music that is right for you. While some radio apps rely on formulas and algorithms, <strong>Samsung Milk Music</strong> leaves it up to your ears to lead your <strong>music</strong> discovery. With one interactive dial, users can quickly scan through 200+ stations programmed by music experts landing on the perfect music for the moment.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Samsung Milk Music App Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/PfrMouEqaSI?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Get Started by Spinning the Dial&nbsp;<br />\nTurn the Dial quickly to jump through genres, slowly to move from station to station</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Create Stations Based on Your Taste<br />\nCreate artist or song-based stations to add more to the mix.</p>\n\n<p>Customize Even More&nbsp;<br />\nMake your stations even better by factoring in what you care about.</p>\n\n<p>Share Your Favorites with Friends<br />\nShare the stations you like across your social network.</p>\n\n<p>Listen Across Your Samsung Devices&nbsp;<br />\nNo matter where you&rsquo;re logged in&mdash;on <strong><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\">your phone</a></strong>, gear, or tablet&mdash;your listening history and preferences come with you.</p>\n', 'Samsung Electronics Co. Ltd', 'September 9, 2015', 124133, 'ON', 'none'),
(49, 'Lybrate - Consult a Doctor', 'android', 'Varies with device', 'Varies with device', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lybrate.phoenix&hl=en', 'download.jpg', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/9HZ9GzIiF7-c_7AI4G8r18wpKlKu8VVY6J2iNjCrOyssjQ-gGPUgsibq2tuT84yq9U0=h310-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/j1GBJT3_qSCSu_kD28TW8-ny6PZG3M7gmKLngXwfdFn_mBcN0NRZwD_CLsJxa9VZ2z7_=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LeqGKKjwIi8MR-By-8YHr0zoxrdkXJwZlN22GiOmxVPFNKosy6S_gFlbnpEw7LU5-g=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/2w1g0LCbhy7zAM3Hfbn4OIpXFT31OntEwf19aM9xFw8zouzxd4y7a09v_CkoCEpGyqE=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GuIQSt521QYcTIF_2w4VhOwJfKxMno4hWCJnT1KxJ0AYP2SYgcPeLh8iuuuyuLutams=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/v_qWpURBA3CcWvJZjj4AkxdBYMmqSqBum9WOYYwtFM71UbPEND05PRUNweDIzA657xE=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pvRe7IzmtAS5gOBuqActlGx3O32ieDqZv-wMfkjv7WnXMJhNJDlV_0vFt_mA62S_atU=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hq-PEw8t64-g8t8VcPYnSog22PwbsrYjjyClM9pB68fasRiPCjvdnZdXMpK1tiNNxg=h900-rw\">\n[END_IMAGE]\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Lybrate?</strong></h2>\n\n<p><strong>Lybrate</strong> is your clinic in your pocket with 24/7 access to your patient data. Beautifully designed and ultra-simple to use, <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=49\"><strong>Lybrate</strong></a> lets you add patients, create appointments, track payments, record patient treatments and more, all with a few swipes. You will be surprised that it lets you do so many things. And because it lets you do so many things so easily.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Lybrate</strong> automatically keeps all your information synced between your PC and android so you can use Lybrate as a standalone Practice manager or in conjunction with the web platform. Lybrate has been designed for Doctors by Doctors.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Lybrate App Review&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/OeKL_KaYht4?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>Features:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Find Doctors: Find and book <strong>appointments online</strong> with doctors. Find doctor online in Delhi NCR, Mumbai, Chennai, Kolkata, Pune, Bangalore, Hyderabad, Chandigarh, and other major cities of India.</li>\n	<li>Ask Health Questions: Ask doctor your health-related questions anonymously in an open forum or privately to the trusted doctor of your choice. Get answers to your ask doctor your health queries from qualified doctors.</li>\n	<li>Get Multiple Opinions: Post your health-related questions in an open forum and get many trusted doctors from the concerned specialty answer those.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Virtual Consultation: Discuss your health issues privately with the doctor of your choice. You can also add your doctor here and do routine stuff like showing medical reports, asking for diet plans, and other consultation right from the cozy comfort of your home. You can pay from here and get the right consultation whenever you need it.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Daily Health Tips: Get precious health tips and suggestions on a wide range of health issues from trusted doctors.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Know About Trends: Learn about the prevalent diseases and endemics in your area and the world over and ways of avoiding those from doctors.</li>\n	<li>Personalized Plans from Doctors: Get disease-specific healing tips from your doctor to heal better at home. A feature extremely useful for pregnant women, people undergone some kind of surgery, physiotherapy patients, and the likes in which every day care is critical.</li>\n	<li>Manage Medical Records: You don&rsquo;t need to manage those messy paper records anymore. Click a photo and upload your documents on the cloud to access those anytime anywhere.</li>\n	<li>Connect with Doctors: Connect with top doctors from all over India on various issues. Learn about diseases and conditions, and ask your health-related queries.</li>\n	<li>Do this all for FREE.</li>\n</ul>\n', 'Lybrate', 'September 7, 2015', 104898, 'ON', 'none'),
