(53, 'Cleartrip', 'ios', 'Varies with device', 'Varies with device', '1', 'http://www.apxadtracking.net/iclk/redirect.php?apxcode=658665&id=eTbRmTjngTuwD3jneTJnKUbXD3xMgT4HKUbn&dv1=', 'icon175x175.png', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"Cleartrip\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/b9Uu_rM06CW7Ri-c7UH4UPBEu8ey42V1n-RuSHMpNTokfylo2yQUXAPaR50vZNZXWpBi=h310-rw\" style=\"height:294px; width:165px\" /><img alt=\"Cleartrip android\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/JAYGpsqO5YDhi0eTGL1WeBsBAI86kxfs5HvwvfFQaV0eBAHnjJkukoiYJCdyHVXyVSU=h310-rw\" style=\"height:294px; width:165px\" /><img alt=\"Cleartrip android\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Xoz9M32DpeRnDromD69fFeMdZO5iwPa4hMdBG3zOqHOBzl9cqZMvVnmaa3tniQQpEQw0=h310-rw\" style=\"height:294px; width:165px\" /></p>\n\n<h2>What is&nbsp;Cleartrip</h2>\n\n<p>Book trains, flights, hotels and experiences. Travel was never so simple. &nbsp;Download the app and get Rs. 250 cashback with the coupon code APPTRIP (Applicable once on flight &amp; hotel bookings) &nbsp;More than 6 million people love to use Cleartrip on mobile to plan, search and book their trips. Save time and money when booking flights, trains (authorised by IRCTC), hotels and unique experiences with amazing deals and the best experience around.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\">Video&nbsp;Cleartrip App Review</h2>\n\n<p>Travel<br />\n<br />\n- Search and book trains across all classes, between all stations, at the same prices offered by IRCTC (iPhone only)<br />\n- Check PNR status of your waitlisted bookings and live running status of any train<br />\n- Easily view train availability and schedules with our unique train calendar<br />\n<br />\n- Search and book domestic and international flights<br />\n- Choose from hundreds of domestic and international airlines<br />\n- Sort and filter by price, arrival/departure times and your favourite airline to find the perfect flight<br />\n<br />\nStay<br />\n<br />\n- Search and book rooms in hotels in more than 15,000 cities cross the world<br />\n- Save up to 50% and more with app exclusive hotel deals<br />\n- Exclusive last-minute deals for same-day and next-day check-ins<br />\n- Pay@Hotel: Book your room on Cleartrip and pay directly at the hotel<br />\n- Free cancellations for most hotels in India<br />\n- Use price, star rating, traveller rating and location filters to quickly find the best stay<br />\n- A beautiful hotel booking experience, designed specifically for couch surfing on your iPad<br />\n<br />\nExperience<br />\n<br />\n- For the first time in India, instantly book more than 5000 handpicked &amp; curated activities in 25 cities across India<br />\n- Discover amazing experiences &amp; find your passion, be it in your city or on a trip<br />\n- Harley Davidson rides, kids workshops, food tours or learning new skills, there is something for everyone<br />\n- Microlight flying in Bangalore, Scuba diving in Goa, Yachting in Mumbai, Pub hopping in Kolkata; you name it and we have it<br />\n<br />\nYour personal travel assistant<br />\n<br />\n- Carry your trips with you wherever you go in you Passbook and travel paperless<br />\n- Stay updated on your upcoming trips on your Apple Watch<br />\n- Manage your trips on the go with in-app cancellations and flight rescheduling<br />\n- Pay using whatever option suits you: credit card, debit card, net banking or popular wallets like Paytm<br />\n- See fares in all major currencies like USD, GBP, EUR, SGD and more<br />\n- Customers in GCC countries (Bahrain, Kuwait, Oman, Qatar, Saudi Arabia and UAE) may make payment in their local currencies</p>\n', 'Cleartrip', 'September 19, 2015', 165042, 'ON', 'none'),
(56, 'Amazon Shopping', 'android', 'Varies with device', 'Varies with device', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.amazon.mShop.android.shopping&hl=en', 'fafa.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/e8ImFEd8Wc_FQJz0VH9tTeizmSMK49YEiVMZlaRXu-FvGirKkOazFl9Jxc4uSjciCi4=h310-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/yfwWXAz1GsxEta_Sk25FVYO8Gi-LlCpVhVo-J7Efdt4R6BsCE7e0II1zgs0aAPEHb9M=h310-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/8BhoVeE0gAVHZUnw_xB4KMzrDXYR8jhMdzxNucXDTHM5cB5IbTAqHL_XLZVo2p2YQ-4=h310-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/O9yrG6pn94MHggfm_gv1SPA0rdJBGOqrcoRn4JCCO1-Qz3_BZpnk5ZE2VXCfzPH2OCfE=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/NzxMVJnyf_tAPVPqtt--D_ncjsdEWNJn-EsDYuxBxsEwNInpnF4CIxtm8e7OZ3iL5rw=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/W6fdSO_SdIUZWRxwGUhPWBNvmgTq4DdRmXRxyubXFmm3AascsqMcCQM1U2Ek0A6_smc=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/HofsAaonzxJoeat36zgCEN6XmQBD14gMGeP_kWGJ5Fysn_TeRTGhbO0bRlYIBK0tpr0F=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/pPuYNz8STyORmnTPzuz-NT9wmj1_WU0qf60BfVrsrd9egQy_oFtRrWO6_flQ_NsyVt0=h900-rw\">[END_IMAGE]\n<h2><strong>What is Amazon shopping?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=56\"><strong>Amazon app</strong></a> allows you to quickly make purchases, search, compare prices, read reviews, and share products with friends using a simple yet elegant interface. Shop just as you do on the web. You can access any of Amazon&#39;s sites around the world from a single app by simply selecting your desired <strong>Amazon</strong> country store or shipping destination. You have full access to your existing cart and wish lists. Search for products using the Amazon app, and easily add them to your <strong>shopping cart</strong> to purchase.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\">Video&nbsp;Amazon Shopping App Review&nbsp;</h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Bh8VjB-swuU?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>Product Features</p>\n\n<p>* Customers are able to shop millions of products on any of <strong>Amazon&#39;s sites</strong> around the world from a single app<br />\n* Quickly search, get product details, and read reviews on millions of products from Amazon and other merchants<br />\n* Take advantage of 1-Click ordering, customer support, Wish Lists, create or find a baby or wedding registry, order tracking, and more<br />\n* Scan product barcodes and images to compare prices and check availability using Scan It&nbsp;<br />\n* Check out Gold Box Deals - including the Deal of the Day and Lightning Deals, and get automatically notified when new deals become available<br />\n* Customers with an <strong><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\">Android</a> </strong>Wear smart watch can search with their voice, 1-Click buy products, and save products and ideas to their Wish List<br />\n* Send and share links to products via email, SMS, Facebook, Twitter, and more<br />\n* Sign-up for automatic shipment notifications to know when your order ships and arrives<br />\n* Buy with confidence, knowing that all transactions are securely processed<br />\n* Use your voice to search for products on Amazon or to track your orders and reorder items. Tap the microphone icon and say &ldquo;track order&rdquo; or &ldquo;track my last order&rdquo; to access open orders. Reorder products by saying &ldquo;reorder paper towels&rdquo; or &ldquo;buy more batteries&rdquo;.</p>\n', 'Amazon Mobile LLC', 'September 2, 2015', 153093, 'ON', 'none'),
