(83, 'Clash Of Clans', 'android', '47M', '7.200.19', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.supercell.clashofclans&hl=en', 'sfs.png', '<div class=\"thumbnail\"><span class=\"pre\" style=\"display:none\"></span><span class=\"next\" style=\"display:block\"></span><div class=\"list\" style=\"width: 5100px;\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/thvHUL5qKGE1_IjiemridPQ-T3N8w0BrjRTJyr1zeKKdbnpqNqqtPGuav3jaugVmXGY=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/Y-60cpKr1IlLrN22HDsN74dlfKNsVrbRuj_X5yF6Ik-AwVY8xnlJIM0rgDeYzTgYCo-K=h900-rw\" alt=\"Clash of Clans\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/Pwav0vrkvYxVClt356QEDiJ19qonYJIa5dGKDp0xhQ-tN2cSizXjm6OiRUam1xRa_Q=h900-rw\" alt=\"Clash of Clans\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/EYd1XRhZbVWg15XZe0K5seT9ikAkhpvtuDxAja1QjsVJg4yM5jiTNTgZfiJPsfTDfw=h900-rw\" alt=\"Clash of Clans\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/HU6IV_2V_uo79jhAP-LTjvzbM_6OK8xBC71bCj6igIn_LepPw6cngcqm_-TZCXfD-g=h900-rw\" alt=\"Clash of Clans\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/1Nr4Omc6Kgze9SsWM5q_d8nji--T-KF5cvcyMLwQGh3kDj2IazohMstiRY54JNhOgmXI=h900-rw\" alt=\"Clash of Clans\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/uYdjVgp8eJwmov8QxukFse_xpe9ulu-iD--ZIl-nwfnF6uboLhUAzsjKd4E_ZK_lxSk=h900-rw\" alt=\"Clash of Clans\">[END_IMAGE]\n\n<h2><strong>What is clash of clans?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>From rage-&shy;filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a <strong>powerful clan</strong> with others to destroy enemy clans.</p>\n\n<p>PLEASE NOTE! <strong>Clash of Clans</strong> is free to download and play, however some <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\"><strong>game</strong></a> items can also be purchased for real money. If you do not want to use this feature, please set up password protection for purchases in the settings of your Google Play Store app. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=83\"><strong>download Clash of Clans</strong></a>.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Clash Of Clans Game Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/RJzXl5BUfEM?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>A network connection is also required.</p>\n\n<p>FEATURES<br />\nâ— Build your village into an unbeatable fortress&nbsp;<br />\nâ— Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters<br />\nâ— Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies<br />\nâ— Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan<br />\nâ— Fight against rival Clans in epic <strong>Clan Wars</strong>&nbsp;<br />\nâ— Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades<br />\nâ— Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements&nbsp;<br />\nâ— Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls<br />\nâ— Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm</p>\n', 'Supercell', 'October 2, 2015', 362148, 'ON', 'none'),
(84, 'MakeMy Trip', 'android', '15M', '5.2.8', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.makemytrip&hl=en', 'rs.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/jFtYqhTpxqJ4HnVDMIrm-GJRUug1riIkKwDXR64KdbqPZTNuFmV5gCaLrhdOugxbIQ=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Al_Hqli01lAOGxbglZkn3sbWjnLzyrkds4wWlxjW6DzQK73R3x16Yw2eh7JOnMfSlA=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/0JcoJCVPpWrYFNiVb4k0hiP_R-A_EQR1e-idwpNRbnV3NiCy2h_YDZ72oRzM5gwSGew=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/cHg2SXcJe9Kdl5DURzkTlILSd_WQnZ0V4mSjiHFPbcD_CsaGUgKCOsdwkWGSviFgxDSn=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/w3ooImF-g8I0qe-0YkbhTTAZQ8GeUjt8oG5rrLfBy3tJKcol4YXyJHIM8pchN3mdnw=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/k7V6K4jmK5RnFIcaOGe-CqVn7p1xZErFJEhxshrmc-X3uOJxpkeVuysmx5jpgxuyr28=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/_MlK4U3LfPJdTtK7DyAajC0ReWKZgCtgb9KMZhhsAp4YU9jVCHk5UBOVVeKKQEtUM4c=h900-rw\">[END_IMAGE]\n\n<h2><strong>What is makemy trip?</strong></h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=84\"><strong>makemytrip&nbsp;app</strong></a> is&nbsp;travel app ordering largest online india.</p>\n\n<p>Flight Bookings<br />\n- <strong>Travel </strong>within India and abroad<br />\n- Cheapest flight tickets for one-way and round trips on domestic and international flights<br />\n- Great discounts on round trip flight bookings<br />\n- Store your latest flight search preferences&nbsp;<br />\n- Featured domestic airlines: Indigo, Jet Airways, Air India, Spice Jet, Jet lite, Jet Airways, Indigo, Indian Airlines, Go Air, Air Costa, Air Asia, Vistara and Air India Express<br />\n- Featured international airlines: Kuwait Airways, Qatar Airways, Malaysia Airlines, Thai Airways, British Airways, Air Arabia, Emirates, Etihad, Singapore Air, Lufthansa, Air Arabia, Cathay Pacific, Saudi Arabian Airlines, American Airlines, Delta Airlines, Continental Airlines</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;makemy trip app review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/qt0wsYmsRVQ?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>Hotel Bookings (powered by tripadvisor Ratings)<br />\n- Easy to search hotel information<br />\n- Book a cheap hotel of your choice in India and the world&rsquo;s best cities<br />\n- Get up to 45% discount on online hotel bookings<br />\n- No credit card? Don&rsquo;t worry. Now, you can pay for your booking at the hotel itself! Search hotel information and book easily<br />\n- Exclusive deals for users logged in via <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=42\"><strong>Facebook</strong></a>, Google or <strong>MakeMyTrip</strong> account<br />\n- Tripadvisor ratings and tripadvisor reviews to help you choose your hotel</p>\n\n<p>Bus Bookings<br />\n- Book bus tickets across 12,000 bus routes and with over 1,300 bus operators in India&nbsp;<br />\n- Choose from the widest range of available buses like Mercedes, Volvo, Volvo AC, AC luxury, Deluxe, Sleeper, Express and other private buses</p>\n\n<p>IRCTC Authorized Rails Booking<br />\n- Search for all available trains&nbsp;<br />\n- Your one stop point for railway ticket booking<br />\n- IRCTC Railway ticket booking (general and tatkal) on all major routes in India</p>\n\n<p>PNR Status<br />\n- Know your PNR status easily after your train <strong>booking</strong><br />\n- PNR status is available for tickets booked with us<br />\n- PNR status is regularly updated</p>\n\n<p>Manage Trips&nbsp;<br />\n- Access all your flight and hotel bookings through MakeMyTrip&nbsp;<br />\n- View booking details, make cancellations, request e-tickets and much more<br />\n- Manage your holiday without any hassles</p>\n\n<p>One-touch Booking<br />\n- Save your card details for a hassle-free holiday booking experience<br />\n- To ensure safe and secure transactions while booking your holiday, <strong>MakeMyTri</strong>p is protected by SSL technology by VeriSign, the leaders in encryption technology</p>\n\n<p>Fast, Safe, Secure<br />\n- Enjoy a fast booking experience even on 2G connection<br />\n- To ensure security of your information, MakeMyTrip has taken PCI DSS compliance certification. PCI DSS is the payment card industry security requirement for entities that store, process or transmit cardholder data, and has been endorsed by all the major card brands&mdash;Visa Inc., MasterCard Worldwide, Discover Network, American Express and JCB.</p>\n', 'MakeMyTrip.com', 'October 27, 2015', 135062, 'ON', 'none'),
(85, 'Colopl Rune Story', 'ios', '38M', '1.0.28', '0', 'https://itunes.apple.com/ph/app/colopl-rune-story/id1010987911?mt=8', 'sdaf.jpg', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/IEpvAGWCWY51JmCG3Ppbnmz_IId6Hgi5EG30Rh8Oco479_iZCUl0tGTRx78N3DFIRt3T=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/eO-MPhl89ry-0g3_oBhWBedIzVArrRw7S2nUDSoygnYQBrL1TuZY90vgV2JmEC0k8z6_=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LBbpy1WgJN-qWsS9u1XKv_KCeULyK2fRZYpWLCrL7cUDs9OG7igcyGJD1nlrbodVV8U=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/WQl6Gy1YhUf7ltptF5h6jnO7-3TXdQD4cngu8pC2gfDOMsFtImuUNdIY-WuG-REASfI=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/FMp7T_dvJiogssOGDj47tSkrKzkafdBHwaE9AxdChuS9AJurKdJMKsSsnz7awj0O8iQ=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/kZSx2b-swHlVR21k0JX87dj79Py_pahmy7sgdd2rey6uGXoI1tk3u3ycH8ETLAUuqlZI=h900-rw\">[END_IMAGE]\n\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Colopl Rune Story?</strong></h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=85\"><strong>Colopl Rune Story</strong></a> is now out worldwide for <strong>iOS</strong> and Android and is free to download. It&rsquo;s a blend of RPG, city-building, and resource-management that developer Colopl says is a more Western-friendly take on its action-RPG White Cat Project.</p>\n\n<p>The <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\"><strong>game&rsquo;s story</strong></a> goes like this:</p>\n\n<p>From the flying island of Astora to the final destination of &lsquo;The World&rsquo;s End,&rsquo; players must use a mystical rune compass to uncover ancient magical runesthat fell from the sky centuries ago. Recruiting and training hundreds of characters, joining forces with other players, as well as building a town from which to harvest resources and upgrade weaponry are key to leading a strong army.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Colopl Rune Story Game Review&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/xRTZKkb9nQ0?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>* Real-Time Co-Op Action RPG *<br />\nPerform magnificent combo attacks that will surpass regular puzzle-solving, dragon-fighting <strong>games</strong> and control all movements, actions, and skills from the palm of one hand.</p>\n\n<p>* Over 100+ Unique Characters to Play *<br />\nUnlock hundreds of characters and weapon combinations within six classes - Fencer, Lancer, Warrior, Brawler, Sniper, Mage.</p>\n\n<p>* Fight Epic Bosses With Your Guild *<br />\nBecome the strongest guild! Accumulate Guild Points in co-op quests to obtain special rewards.</p>\n\n<p>* Build Your Own Unique Town *<br />\nBuild and upgrade your town to harvest resources to level up and train your team.</p>\n\n<p>Legend has it that runes imbued with ancient magic fell from seven elder runes in the sky centuries ago, but few remain. Airships fly the skies between the flying island Astora and the world&rsquo;s other countless islands. Use the wondrous rune compass to guide your path as you attempt to uncover magical runes and journey to The World&rsquo;s End, a place no one has ever reached.</p>\n', 'COLOPL NI, INC.', 'October 2, 2015', 165074, 'ON', 'none'),
(86, 'Agent Alice', 'ios', 'Vary by device', '4.0.3 and up', '0', 'https://itunes.apple.com/en/app/agent-alice/id938120844?mt=8', 'jfklaf.png', '<div class=\"thumbnail\"><span class=\"pre\" style=\"display:none\"></span><span class=\"next\" style=\"display:block\"></span><div class=\"list\" style=\"width: 5100px;\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/OerxV4K9vmxtD30Oj4cmcCK-SHdCKy-NCsRH4Nndq9Q8JhMZ7Ztu7QxQN6FcNYMkLzyg=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/3XS49cIwbV1Uqu9TF8cqqnDCk5Eo3d1C3Is0CNpoVDA6-bKdNXuBf1LlGLO2lSZFHwM=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/h4GGms3-Rmb9kKgfl_FIlqjnT85iLDnwQAVZifgXSu79lp21nu3UP-p4TfqJUdjr4oQ=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/dEpoSyVPVApyVk802bWfguxMt97izxu9h9-eojzFDVFA2Qwq9bVrj_luDQ4aCql1zYU=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/Aq8_WZ_8IU35WZfMAdMUWtFwfIRAYMCZS-I-1_3Y1DdPHSJ9dJJUZuR2NxCo3LIGpA=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/YWhxw5gGnPo_B2bL3GC-oHctAELL4XVlRv64HIh6UY8VojcyBHloxHrb1qRL9IDTbNg=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/sp6NvsZ7K_U2_RZCSlIqmIQW_Yrc0_Ye76iQnbpn1Kptl2HxurjoJ6gpodQCLTFZjdk=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/rNYQHmy81GSanHtLIttWwaDjX4MRy4UUquO8_QVPE5q9eVQtXFz6xwyuFdXg6PpVWw=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/NpSS9HkHs1QWRP8fwtiPl9ujNmqP6kXmVkP3hfzk-yQUHZx3qpfc8XOaGqXrlG8qJMI=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/blLdgBs4u_KoAKdqX-_3zUhtL6Gr6-O81swAuD617cz9eqmyPQoc64F6vlTctgTUh_8=h900-rw\" alt=\"Agent Alice\">[END_IMAGE]\n<h2><strong>What is Agent Alice?</strong></h2>\n\n<p><strong>Agent Alice</strong>&nbsp;- investigate cases of mysterious crimes. Find important clues and other hidden objects to solve different puzzles. Use your logic and observation skills to help the beautiful heroine of this <strong>Android game</strong>, Special <strong>Agent Alice</strong> Wallace, in her investigations. Go to the crime scene and have a look around. Find the clues left by the villain. Follow the trail of the criminal and move from one location to another. Crack ciphers and codes, solve challenging logic puzzles.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video Game Agent Alice Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/bOwKpZXRabc?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>*WHY YOU&rsquo;LL LOVE<strong> AGENT ALICE</strong>*<br />\nâ— JOIN THE TEAM &ndash; Find out what Agent Alice and her team are up to every week in brand-new hidden object episodes.<br />\nâ— NEW PUZZLE STYLES &ndash; It&rsquo;s not just hidden object games. You&rsquo;ll have to use all your puzzling skill with matching, action and reaction <strong>games </strong>galore!<br />\nâ— PLAY IN BEAUTIFUL SURROUNDINGS &ndash; Brand new content every week, with thrilling new action, romance, rivalries and adventure.<br />\nâ— GET TRANSPORTED BACK TO THE SWINGING 60s &ndash; With the highest quality hand-drawn artwork, you&rsquo;ll experience the romance and adventure of stunning locations all over the world, right at the height of their beauty.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Agent Alice</strong> is free to download and play, but it also allows you to purchase virtual items with real money inside the <strong>game</strong>. You can disable in-app purchases in your device&rsquo;s settings.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Wooga', 'September 8, 2015', 163059, 'ON', 'none'),
