//www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/BbFXG-rgha0?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Game Features:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>âœ”Hero Evolution - Enter the battlefield with cooler and stronger Heroes than before!<br />\nâœ” Here Be Demons! Take on the new boss with your friends!&nbsp;<br />\nâœ” Defend your bases with others in co-op combat!<br />\nâœ” Build and upgrade your impenetrable fortress!<br />\nâœ” Create the ultimate army from a dozen wild troops!<br />\nâœ” Fast-paced, thrilling, and realistic battles!<br />\nâœ” Pit your Heroes against other Players in the Arena!<br />\nâœ”Create your very own Guild and lead it to victory in Guild Wars!<br />\nâœ” Join other players and conquer Team Dungeons!<br />\nâœ” Tap and swipe to cast powerful spells!<br />\nâœ” Free-to-play fantasy strategy.</p>\n', 'IGG.COM', 'November 12, 2015', 236533, 'ON', 'none'),
(91, 'Clash Of Kings', 'android', '47M', '1.1.13', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hcg.cok.gp&hl=en', 'Ã¡dgdfgdf.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/zjU9YKK_w3INbvqhd0OPKsi2D4D9899TXi6WzQDl2gezjIdl3-jw66qeiX0sCpFGdlN4=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/VI1NQ_n0DIFWvtNIC7aIjFdZfhgVIzvJF2nWGGA2EsmlKTBzgTdlx5UYOLB8e8QMdA=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Lfz8QBoCkXxPlMDHOTdr2Jgw40NrKacler-e0NPC4RTRY0tiZr3jklHaNRSrUx7Qbcw=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/8cpGvybt5IvkHSbyAQAUALmPnC8fd4XN1QQGBhoJKaB6EUOdXkSyCzZWI3-NGK7VHz0=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/CZkVJ1D1Ed0QyLpRkOjHNuafGcyyijSWUeMe5Cog-edfRaTTbyieHAJozGvk7KPZcSg=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/2J9D440XuUMZ_QWeaJLy-wJZYKUFX0Rs67OOzpS33YNU4qIFf2q1R2gQKbu0-pESD3A=h900-rw\">[END_IMAGE]\n<h2><strong>What is Clash Of Kings?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>Build massive cities and compete in online multiplayer battles in a classic <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=83\"><strong>clash of clans</strong></a>. Reinforce your city and build your town to be strong enough to defend itself against evil lords and armies threatening to invade.<br />\nAre you ready to join thousands of other clans in a war to control kingdoms? Build up your army, battle enemies and manage your city&rsquo;s resources to become one of the most powerful lords of all in <strong>Clash of Kings</strong> &ndash; Last Empire!<br />\nBuild your city and prepare for action</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Clash Of Kings Game Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/J_R_Pbizxq8?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>Run a King&rsquo;s Empire in this PVP Action Adventure!<br />\nâ˜† Use your best real time PVP strategy to win the war! Clash of Kings is a multiplayer strategy <strong>war game</strong> all about sending your fighting army against your enemies&rsquo; empire.</p>\n\n<p>Free to Play: Multiplayer Online PVP war<br />\nâ˜† Empire allies ramp up the PVP action! Join one for protection, deception, to build an empire or to grow your army. Use your fighting army to fight other players online from all around the world! In this real time strategy war game you&rsquo;ll rise through the ranks to have the strongest kings empire!</p>\n\n<p>Build Massive Empires to Defend a Tower Rush<br />\nâ˜† Your fantasy kingdom needs both a strong offense and castle defense. <strong>Clash of Kings </strong>lets you build massive empires with upgradable buildings and tons of medieval tricks so you can defend your kingdom against an enemy tower rush. Who will attack first, you or your enemies?</p>\n\n<p>Vivid Fantasy Empire Graphics<br />\nâ˜† The beautiful scenery and art in Clash of Kings makes playing in this fantasy realm an epic war adventure! Explore the world of endless empires and kingdoms!</p>\n\n<p>Clash of Kings PVP Multiplayer Game Features:<br />\nâ˜† Real time strategy <strong>multiplayer games</strong> and battles! Build an empire and clash with your enemies in a free fantasy kingdom!<br />\nâ˜† Gather resources as you build massive empires. Defense against a tower rush is as important attacking an enemy empire.<br />\nâ˜† SimCity like city building of your king&rsquo;s empire! Defend your empire through strong battle strategy! Build a massive empire to build up your army!<br />\nâ˜†Enjoy the battle games and PVP action on your <strong>mobile phone</strong> or tablet! Clash of Kings supports both!</p>\n', 'Elex Wireless', 'October 2, 2015', 296357, 'ON', 'none'),
(92, 'Asphalt 8: Airborne', 'android', '76.3M', '2.3 and up ', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gameloft.android.ANMP.GloftA8HM&hl=en', 'asphalt 8.png', '<div class=\"thumbnail\"><span class=\"pre\" style=\"display:none\"></span><span class=\"next\" style=\"display:block\"></span><div class=\"list\" style=\"width: 5100px;\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/kxHECgKzLtPMGYT8TcxNOVUZB7m3aRxmpz3FP7krWaFoCsA4KxU7zOIpThthNr55Xf4=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/cmOu4NLBjqfpHwHgIAef_qu-Jw0ArMt5xiksvaCaRY778YR1rBxMAah9egK3NjLJrQ=h900-rw\" alt=\"Asphalt 8\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/8amAmW6zxjuC9J5U3ZpmOqsXtUGbvJhaY7enq1ukC9ybk4Ctl3NrOqOXsKg9fe19MBDP=h900-rw\" alt=\"Asphalt 8\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/aCij7vikrvpfk6bjkPT2unq9zabdyQu2uFQGWA6RiRyiFoa9cZ7msKXShQj0P70I9sY=h900-rw\" alt=\"Asphalt 8\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/orzFJjK1l2TZpaYF3H7WVt4okBg0v7GRMUVq7fDXCBkJsWglzuhAteP47jFAD5QQ6A=h900-rw\" alt=\"Asphalt 8\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/sqvegUoY05dISMsxxwA5F48t_AfdhT1Htkw3xNdF8gB21GS8niBqNPxzmDEn1MsFsdBE=h900-rw\" alt=\"Asphalt 8\">[END_IMAGE]\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Asphalt 8?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>The best <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\"><strong>Android</strong></a> arcade racing <strong>game series</strong> reaches a new turning point! Perform dynamic, high-speed aerial stunts in an <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=92\"><strong>intense driving</strong></a> experience powered by a brand-new physics engine!</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video &nbsp;Asphalt 8 Game Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/ACLtiJ2qar4?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>LUXURY DREAM CARS&nbsp;<br />\n&bull; More than 95 high-performance cars (80% of them NEW!)<br />\n&bull; Top licensed manufacturers and models like Lamborghini Veneno, Bugatti Veyron, Ferrari FXX and Pagani Zonda R, <strong>Lamborghini Aventador</strong> and <strong>Audi R8</strong> LMS Ultra<br />\n&bull; Newly recorded high-fidelity car motor sounds for realistic audio immersion</p>\n\n<p>GET AIRBORNE<br />\n&bull; Hit the ramps and take the race above<br />\n&bull; Perform barrel rolls and wild 360&ordm; jumps&nbsp;<br />\n&bull; Maneuver through the air, pulling stunts while racing</p>\n\n<p>NEW EXOTIC LOCATIONS<br />\n&bull; Race in 13 different settings like Venice, San Diego Harbor, Iceland, the Nevada Desert, Dubai and other exciting locations!&nbsp;<br />\n&bull; All tracks available in original and mirror variations in Career mode<br />\n&bull; Discover plenty of hidden shortcuts</p>\n', 'Gameloft', 'October 9, 2015', 403683, 'ON', 'none'),
(93, 'Bejeweled Blitz', 'android', '47M', '1.14.2.57', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ea.BejeweledBlitz_na&hl=en', 'BejeweledBlitz.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/gI-hSdnSkdz3AXoZpBucAxKUadjnEsyT2ykWnp3NMGER3TNtaZOmazsJpZhDZAq6zqM=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/0hHkf75PquLJ9EIZB4COoKZGVofX0W1R7hVFOpUPEddTraRcQUTaa8w5jTcsq-imdQ=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/FbaWSpSzU543lofZxmeaR6dY6pEDNKXZ7LX1MPjGsob8daG5sq3T1Z-S0a5W-vvuly1-=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/TACDd_XG6AZ1YD8YSo6yjc1MdPMAm0jhjBI6SYbczmQG5N15rIg3x_DvbuUbZo43JOU=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/delHRMQTa7N640tyhX7Wy9m224zu-im4VjpZWIIk-DIrL9RJR8dncLAt8Rl7_C6Vx6mx=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/QtKmz4xk2UUF7nIWQvWVpJ86LL0YDZZxs88ygxD9onx4O7hJvFwqTGZLqnXt4t8j7Q=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/-9t4zxW5loNWiCm4SLeAMc8S_cUcBlWEkk_QGhDx235ygj77BZBbcJJ0Zrhyvq1oTw0=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/_cuAct205lzajqix67ABaqx_FYTTt9asNOH4kfYSV4-dQoa9GTL8YMXy5zLu9wyuxxc=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/GEQioBXBRUnrOteAlmRQhQQkOcxVkmT19HA885VDrnijLjkvxN8tMinMs31fea4UJeE=h900-rw\">[END_IMAGE]\n\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Bejeweled Blitz?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>Enjoy one minute of endless match-3 fun from <strong>PopCap</strong> &ndash; and <strong>play for free!</strong> Detonate as many gems as you can in 60 action-packed seconds and compete with <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=42\"><strong>Facebook</strong></a> friends. Match three or more and create cascades of awesome with <strong>Flame gems</strong>, Star gems, and Hypercubes. Add up to three Boosts and use powerful Rare Gems to send your score soaring. Try limited-time Rare Gems like Flower Power, Rock-It Blast and others to dominate the weekly leaderboards</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Bejeweled Blitz Game Review</strong>&nbsp;</h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/lKv2txjwqoE?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong><br />\nEASY TO LEARN<br />\nNever played Bejeweled Blitz before? No problem! Our interactive tutorial quickly walks you through the basics to get you ready for all the gem-matching action.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nRARE GEMS<br />\nPropel your score into the stratosphere with the power of Rare Gems, from always-available gems like Kanga Ruby to limited-time gems like Flower Power and Rock-It Blast! And watch for more Rare Gems to keep sending your score soaring.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nEXPLOSIVE EXCITEMENT&nbsp;<br />\nBoost your fun with Detonators, Scramblers and Multipliers. Match as fast as you can to earn Blazing Speed and blow gems away. The &lsquo;Last Hurrah&rsquo; keeps the points piling up even after your time expires.</p>\n\n<p><br />\nROCKET UP THE LEADERBOARD<br />\nChallenge your friends on Facebook to beat your best 60-second score. Own the top spot on your weekly tournament leaderboard. Fill your stats to become the ultimate Bejeweled master and earn bragging rights galore.</p>\n', 'Electronic Arts Inc', 'November 22, 2015', 186065, 'ON', 'none'),
(94, 'Dragon Stadium', 'ios', '97.1M', '1.5', '0', 'https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/dragon-stadium/id972605153?mt=8', 'Dragon Stadium.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"http://a4.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/b9/cb/29/b9cb290d-b055-1086-7d5a-79a9ea93bd75/screen322x572.jpeg\">\n<img src=\"http://a5.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/41/c1/41/41c14179-fd06-13df-c063-f8cbe09eed01/screen322x572.jpeg\">\n<img src=\"http://a3.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/7c/3a/e2/7c3ae27f-fde3-a682-cea5-676362f5f28b/screen322x572.jpeg\">\n<img src=\"http://a4.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/37/d9/48/37d94817-eb9d-0b62-95ba-9933a5b5f386/screen322x572.jpeg\">\n<img src=\"http://a5.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/a5/36/27/a5362798-9059-21f1-abe1-05533b3b93df/screen322x572.jpeg\">[END_IMAGE]\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Dragon Stadium?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>You&#39;re in for an adventure! Enter the world of <strong>Dragon Stadium</strong> and harness its elemental powers to collect an incredible variety of <strong>unique dragons</strong>. Raise them, explore the groups of islands and conquer them all!</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Dragon Stadium Game&nbsp;Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/jpkl7VmBCdA?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n<p><br />\nFEATURES<br />\n- Build your islands and collect dragons of different elements<br />\n- Breed different elemental dragons to obtain the rarest of them all<br />\n- Feed and evolve your <strong>dragons</strong> levelling them up to reach their ultimate power stage<br />\n- Discover the elemental islands and progress on the map to complete all the quests<br />\n- Fight through individual chapters by defeating enemies, collecting coins and ultimately defeating the stage boss<br />\n- Swap between a team of up to three dragons, using the most <strong>powerful elements</strong> against different types of enemies<br />\n- Unlock achievements to get 3 stars and receive all the rewards</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', '', 'Nov 13, 2015', 176536, 'ON', 'none'),
(95, 'Seven Knights', 'ios', '36M', '1.0.14', '0', 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/seven-knights/id970818035?mt=8', 'Seven Knights.png', '<div class=\"thumbnail\"><span class=\"pre\" style=\"display:none\"></span><span class=\"next\" style=\"display:block\"></span><div class=\"list\" style=\"width: 5100px;\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/8mFlKAF6tqZCtPcsy8MXbzmyOVaYqzaj-IAPLFvGCCiVyAwmZYxZw9IZ2EQhLX9kYpZy=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/uIosfSqCcZuyuPN5x0-EWj0rzHJtRAvcnfWEEJ1Uij-c4Du0ZC8Qsy7-c_wzcvtdcvVW=h900-rw\" alt=\"Seven Knights\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/F8-b6zqfb6eZ-pRtXyI0W34_o8lVizaqKgVmR0rjMtyfhmbsErO4AURvHIiAhBMcyQdD=h900-rw\" alt=\"Seven Knights\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/JBtpClJg2phX_QD_Xgpjq-BudW46yvwVsKfx2YYyP1AfE63EjRRFbVMvX9rKTLqLlJI=h900-rw\" alt=\"Seven Knights\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/XKy3ONsLrjbg6Q-fljnNt_E87yMWtkEr42xz7JIpp2a0asOZ-HboXAcUXurz4w36ee7c=h900-rw\" alt=\"Seven Knights\">[END_IMAGE]\n\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Seven Knights?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>stunning RPG filled with heroics, adventure, and a diverse assortment of creatures and fiends.<br />\nThe <strong>land of Ladenberg</strong> is in need of brave warriors who can face the God of Destruction and preserve peace.<br />\nIt is up to you, along with Evan and Karin, to put together a band of warriors to achieve victory</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video Seven Knights Game Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/SxZX1cIv2Gc?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>FEATURES</p>\n\n<p>LIMITLESS 3D BATTLES<br />\n- Enlist teams by combining hundreds of heroes for powerful combinations<br />\n- Immerse yourself in Dynamic Effects and Diverse Skill Animations</p>\n\n<p>STRATEGIC PLAY<br />\n- Power Up, Rank Up, and Gear Up to prepare your heroes in their quest for Ladenberg.<br />\n- Customize your Team&#39;s Formation and manage Skills to strategize for the upcoming battles.</p>\n\n<p>NUMEROUS GAME MODES<br />\n- Adventure Mode: Conquer the Continents as you train your <strong>heroes</strong>!<br />\n- Battle Mode: Duel with other players to prove your worth!<br />\n- Celestial Tower: Challenge to your limit as you battle levels of increasing difficulty!<br />\n- Daily Dungeon: Gain a variety of Hero Supplements when you show your strength.<br />\n- Castle Rush: Cooperate with your guild mates to earn the honor of being the Best Guild!</p>\n', 'Netmarble Games', 'October 21, 2015', 213605, 'ON', 'none'),
(96, 'Sky Wars Archon Rises', 'ios', '89.1M', '1.0.11', '0', 'https://itunes.apple.com/ph/app/sky-wars-archon-rises/id897895667?mt=8', 'Sky Wars Archon Rises.png', '<div class=\"thumbnail\"><span class=\"pre\" style=\"display:none\"></span><span class=\"next\" style=\"display:block\"></span><div class=\"list\" style=\"width: 5100px;\">\n<img src=\"http://a3.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple1/v4/a0/53/e3/a053e3f6-7011-de09-ba44-ed9dc44af849/screen640x640.jpeg\">\n<img src=\"http://a3.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple6/v4/8a/a2/0c/8aa20c1c-4518-f16f-6e6c-5134279eb430/screen640x640.jpeg\" alt=\"Sky Wars\">\n<img src=\"http://a4.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/a4/2f/37/a42f3708-146d-431f-1018-15d92d495d38/screen640x640.jpeg\" alt=\"Sky Wars\">\n<img src=\"http://a1.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple4/v4/d4/9e/22/d49e225a-f595-08a2-ba14-300ffa3b9695/screen640x640.jpeg\" alt=\"Sky Wars\">\n<img src=\"http://a5.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple2/v4/a0/a4/0f/a0a40ff7-9770-2e82-5f07-2b5bbf477b20/screen640x640.jpeg\" alt=\"Sky Wars\">[END_IMAGE]\n\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Sky Wars Archon Rises?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>Become a God and wage an epic WAR in the <strong>HEAVENS</strong>. More than a <strong>KING</strong>, you are a DEITY in this 3D MMO strategy game!</p>\n\n<p>Build an EMPIRE, raise an ARMY, and rule the SKY. Heaven awaits someone worthy enough to claim it! <strong>Play Sky Wars</strong>: Archon Rises, the best new <strong>strategy game</strong>!!<br />\nAfter a terrible battle set fire to the world, the throne of heaven lies empty. The last Goddess Ambriel feels you are the one of legend. Players from around the world challenge your divine right, and a dark force stirs in the world below&hellip;</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Sky Wars Archon Rises Game&nbsp;Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/QLxRh1wBc4s?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong><br />\n<br />\nâ†¦ Build and customize your city to reveal the mystery of Archon<br />\nâ†¦ Skill your Archangel hero to increase his power and equip him with powerful artifacts<br />\nâ†¦ Unlock and train Gorgeous 3D combat units<br />\nâ†¦ Raise a powerful army to defeat your enemies<br />\nâ†¦ Strategize your actions and raise your mighty empire to glory<br />\nâ†¦ Fight in empire and alliance tournaments to win great rewards&nbsp;<br />\nâ†¦ Join an alliance, conspire and execute strategies to take over the Throne and become a Mighty King<br />\nâ†¦Capture, tame, and control legendary Monsters and send them to battle to smite your enemies</p>\n', 'Seven Elements Studios, Inc', '14 October 2015', 360380, 'ON', 'none');
