</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video Wechat app review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/rXP1TRswyGg?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center><br>\n<p>WHY USE WECHAT:<br />\n&bull; ALWAYS FREE: No annual subscription fee. Absolutely free for life.<br />\n&bull; FREE VOICE &amp; VIDEO CALLS: High-quality free calls to anywhere in the world.<br />\n&bull; GROUP CHAT: Create group chats with up to 500 people.<br />\n&bull; MULTIMEDIA MESSAGING: Send video, image, text, and voice messages.<br />\n&bull; STICKER GALLERY: Hundreds of free fun, animated stickers to express your feelings from some of your favorite cartoons and movies.<br />\n&bull; MOMENTS: Share your best moments on your personal photo stream.<br />\n&bull; BETTER PRIVACY: WeChat gives you the highest level of control over your privacy. It&rsquo;s the only messaging app to be certified by TRUSTe.<br />\n&bull; MEET NEW FRIENDS: Use &ldquo;Friend Radar&rdquo;, &ldquo;People Nearby&rdquo; and &ldquo;Shake&rdquo; to meet others.<br />\n&bull; ADDICTIVE GAMES: Compete with your friends on some of the hottest games.<br />\n&bull; REALTIME LOCATION: Instead of having to tell others where you are, just use real-time location sharing.<br />\n&bull; LANGUAGE SUPPORT: Localized in 20 different languages and can translate messages to any language<br />\n&bull; AND MORE: Desktop app, custom wallpaper, custom notifications, group walkie-talkie, official accounts.<br />\n&bull; WeRun-WeChat: Aceess HealthKit&nbsp;data&nbsp;and&nbsp;challenge friends&nbsp;tobeat&nbsp;their&nbsp;scores&nbsp;via&nbsp;the &quot;WeRun-WeChat&quot;&nbsp;Official Account.</p>\n', 'Tencent Technology (Shenzhen) Company Limited Â© Tencent Inc.', 'Oct 9, 2015', 216058, 'ON', 'none'),
