>\n\n<p>&bull; Express yourself with text, photos, emoji, emoticons, video, GIFs and Vines.</p>\n\n<p>&bull; Use hashtags (like #NFL) to find more Tweets about topics you love.</p>\n\n<p>&bull; Get closer to people who interest you, including celebrities like Kim Kardashian, Harry Styles and Rihanna.</p>\n\n<p>&bull; <strong>Share Tweets</strong> with apps like Facebook, <strong><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=125\">Whatsapp</a></strong>, Kik, <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=104\"><strong>LINE</strong></a>, email and SMS.</p>\n\n<p>&bull; Tweet links from sites like YouTube, Pinterest, Instagram, Spotify and Pandora.</p>\n\n<p>&bull; Send a private message without limits: now you&#39;re no longer limited to 140 characters when writing a <strong>Direct Message</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>&bull; Now it&#39;s even easier to share a Tweet privately in a Direct Message. Simply press and hold the Tweet you want to share, then pick the people you want to send it to.</p>\n', 'Twitter, Inc. Â© Twitter, Inc.', 'Oct 9, 2015', 265059, 'ON', 'none'),
