(117, 'Dumpster Image & Video Restore', 'android', 'Varies with device', 'Varies with device', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.baloota.dumpster&hl=en', 'dumster.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/CHytPYD09t33AeE8YrsW_Z5DRb0m-r-uD5o0J00GO2ti1XNr_7AEtu1FhZ-YpRIs-iNR=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/znJrq6IRCNrE3N0L_SapYBSIUPPeGDrFtzPyhpVmv9KsdRFLJ0DZRFH4Z4g7DMlMexWZ=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/U4I5nApMzpKv-J6q1zsBVftoQwNZ1xOR4-5aMFT7e3XtaSnIQLvw7V5Q-vNYaxKHIg_4=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/ZzVu5h1_wU4nrcUiFO4AEbj55s2EusZyFJQlsXTE431qbTYa-zEf14G9Yospfrp46gcH=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.ggpht.com/MEk3U2CxZ9Km2ZOgSYLEWZFVg48ZNH7yQGp1eEtvqBz-ty_hQINoZKlCUnO-utsMxA=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/V3js9emkCtHqUK4u7w3c7bF2qmIWjQ0aNR8Ag2f2znJm_o2A2OexXv3xp0H3IdW5y68=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/MeqoQk5NuQwraZakoN3UIWONfdIafJ-m59nLFwLXxss-b5MUhG3p1wirutgK61YAVA=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh6.ggpht.com/M81krYHXL4i24bmRUX_y8l_q1jspmAj3JjD9iIO9NUvWMmmSZCT_I2GLrnu3IuvV8JE=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh4.ggpht.com/Yvqmr2sfyz5nUbrkU1eP-6oGhXjB_ZRqxx9YGhwwfezLrTDhEEJrIY_vT0v8VVchbvg=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh5.ggpht.com/VxStWFwdzL6SNTURjSz3CYd7InPzebIT8HCBWz2sruqv3JIzaJutomdSP7dHmv_TtE88=h900-rw\">\n[END_IMAGE]\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;Dumpster Image &amp; Video Restore?</strong></h2>\n\n<p><strong>Dumpster Image &amp; Video Restore</strong>&nbsp;is an application that, just like the recycling&nbsp;<strong>bin</strong>&nbsp;in Windows, lets you recover the files you delete on your device.&nbsp;Dumpster Image &amp; Video Restore&nbsp;lets you recover all types of files, such as <strong>photographs</strong>, <strong>songs</strong>, <strong>text messages</strong>, documents, and videos. To do this, you just have to touch the files that you want to recover and then confirm. With just two touches on the screen you can recover files on your<strong> mobile phone.</strong></p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;Dumpster Image &amp; Video Restore App Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Z5Wk8BNM6FQ?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Main features:</strong><br />\nâœ” Restore deleted pictures, music files, videos and pretty much almost any file type (pdf, mp3, doc, avi, mp4, jpg, png, rar, ogg, txt and many more:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.google.com/url?q%3Dhttp://dumpsterapp.mobi/support.html%2523file-types%26sa%3DD%26usg%3DAFQjCNE5uh939yTTDejR2E6atUEe8s9fMg&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEVe-NXXiB7mfCpXmQAgf8nV8iv-Q\" target=\"_blank\">http://dumpsterapp.mobi/support.html#file-types</a>)<br />\nâœ” No Rooting needed but if you do, you get improved performance.<br />\nâœ” Internet connection absolutely not required.<br />\nâœ” NEW: Recover uninstalled apps<br />\nâœ” Restore Dumpster backup files with a single tap.<br />\nâœ” Preview deleted photos, videos and audio files before recovering.<br />\nâœ” Send files to Dumpster using &ldquo;share&rdquo; or &ldquo;send to&rdquo; from any file manager or gallery app out there.<br />\nâœ” Scheduled auto-clean of old deleted items.<br />\nâœ” Protect your privacy with a special lockscreen and access restriction.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', 'Baloota', 'October 1, 2015', 149652, 'ON', 'none'),
