(129, 'Viber', 'ios', '85.6M', '5.6.1', '0', 'https://itunes.apple.com/en/app/viber/id382617920?mt=8', 'viber.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Oox3vUT6o26-Jv5IHQYV7p4N4Jpo2wUpOMb5YDGG9sj5L31xUN4Cnh3sk5g2cZtIvA=h310-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/TSwzsChoEl8mzPoZ-zG1esmaOSZlD_RJQY655OwaXCRIiAl6vxNHZvJK5K729IYVnA=h310-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/t3MlQQ1cG-ifpGk81lNBuEjxtamCvi8VE2LXymDf7bWWT9uRTXTkp_RE-iPbRE7wHg=h310-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/6HNd7quHuAxIbMv4Pf2D5F8OX54dPiswr8KtDGwnznrro-VP4-6tgU4vM1chvdeK1N8=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/52fZCUU4qPN7a_8SV_CT5K_lWVFw6C0-gjSRv2nlW64UdnKgBnV9Zg3dQ1rJLErnqLg=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/xma_UnAW2BzAGXd-35tVdvMFatFJTV_w6Bts8bE4uoyd2rRZymqi_RqjeN4ZdCDfV3I=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/TFD0fqkWCBbvZmxlvA9CC9Ktat89y1QTpNwfK5mSbsgK217_YBUlktyOpDEMPI4J-Tvj=h900-rw\">[END_IMAGE]<h2>What is viber?</h2>\n\n<p>viber as messaging applications, chat and make free phone calls.&nbsp;Viber allows you to&nbsp;<strong>make free calls, video chat</strong>, and send free text messages from your Android device to anyone who has the app installed.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\">Video Viber App Review</h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LQXKwuwLQ14?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>On Viber, your phone number is your ID. The app syncs with your mobile contact list, automatically detecting which of your contacts have <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=33\"><strong>Viber</strong></a>.</p>\n\n<p>&bull; Message your friends<br />\n&bull; Make free phone and video calls with HD sound quality<br />\n&bull; Share photos, video messages, voice messages, locations, contact info, rich links, stickers and emoticons<br />\n&bull; Download stickers and animated stickers from the Sticker Market; sort and reorder your stickers.<br />\n&bull; Create group messages with up to 200 participants; manage your group chats as an Admin, editing info and deleting participants.<br />\n&bull; Follow Public Chats &ndash; get on the inside with your favorite personalities; watch their conversations unfold in real-time, &lsquo;like&rsquo; comments and share multi-media content<br />\n&bull; <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\"><strong>Play games</strong></a> with Viber characters, Violet and Legcat; see how many coins you can earn<br />\n&bull; Android Wear support &ndash; send and receive messages from your watch<br />\n&bull; Push notifications guarantee that you never miss a message or call, even when Viber is off<br />\n&bull; Integration with native contact list for calls and messages<br />\n&bull; Support for the Viber Desktop application on Windows and Mac</p>\n', 'Viber Media SARL', 'October 16, 2015', 163099, 'ON', 'none'),
(130, 'WhatsApp Messenger', 'android', '52.1M', 'Varies With Device', '0', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.whatsapp&hl=en', 'whatsapp.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/MMue08byixTw74ST_VkNQDUUJBgVEbjNHDYLhIuHmYhMIMJIp3KjVlnhhqZQOZUtNt8=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/foFmwvVGIwWWXJIukN7png18lFjFgbw3K7BqIm8G-jsFgSTVtkCa-dDkFApUzbvzIvbe=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/iLgMXFO5qEPlTffpI21zaoG51AORnfu8NPb_2SdAXYgOYcb-xDOMfCryPhVvGNjoew=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ElfUPGX67gv0TNQXuDxQGa5a4BYnLAZIgJJmoNoARvqlLQsKEQcNNWz-J_zqGV5vzQ=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/wBgVA58O2xncQkksLatHGoNLI8L6o_1ZM8AC3GCScxCyaDOWOvMsMilaj1Scp3kEOIw=h900-rw\">\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/B9Lc7aFHld7epfMpOcdRnDEDEkZ9ke27Ba61HWCafPEFvznGvKS89R9ftzBAhAIYXGII=h900-rw\">[END_IMAGE]\n<h2>What is&nbsp;WhatApp msssenger?</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=130\"><strong>WhatsApp</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Messenger</strong></a>&nbsp;is the most convenient way of quickly sending messages on your mobile phone to any contact or friend on your contacts list. The only requirement is that the other people must have the app installed on their own device.<br />\n<br />\nCurrently,&nbsp;<strong>WhatsApp</strong>&nbsp;is compatible with just about all mobile operating systems on the market: <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?os=android\"><strong>Android</strong></a>, <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?os=ios\"><strong>iOS</strong></a>, Symbian and Windows Phone. So this basically means you&rsquo;ll be able to use&nbsp;<strong>WhatsApp</strong>&nbsp;to communicate with any friend, regardless of what model of device they have.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\">Video&nbsp;WhatApp msssenger App Review</h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/ynXpu0yIfPM?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>WHY USE WHATSAPP:&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&bull; NO ADDITIONAL FEES: WhatsApp uses your phone&rsquo;s Internet connection (4G/3G/2G/EDGE or Wi-Fi, as available) to message and call friends and family, so you don&rsquo;t have to pay for every message or call.*<br />\n<br />\n&bull; MULTIMEDIA: Send and receive photos, videos, and Voice Messages.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&bull; WHATSAPP CALLING: Call your friends and family using WhatsApp for free, even if they&rsquo;re in another country. WhatsApp calls use your phone&rsquo;s Internet connection rather than your cellular plan&rsquo;s voice minutes.* (Note: you can&rsquo;t access 911 and other emergency service numbers through WhatsApp).&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&bull; GROUP CHAT: Enjoy group chats with your contacts so you can easily stay in touch with your friends or family.<br />\n<br />\n&bull; WHATSAPP WEB: You can also send and receive WhatsApp messages right from your computer&rsquo;s browser.<br />\n<br />\n&bull; NO INTERNATIONAL CHARGES: There&rsquo;s no extra charge to send WhatsApp messages internationally. Chat with your friends around the world and avoid international SMS charges.*&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&bull; SAY NO TO USERNAMES AND PINS: Why bother having to remember yet another username or PIN? WhatsApp works with your phone number, just like SMS, and integrates seamlessly with your phone&rsquo;s existing address book.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&bull; ALWAYS LOGGED IN: With WhatsApp, you&rsquo;re always logged in so you don&rsquo;t miss messages. No more confusion about whether you&rsquo;re logged in or logged out.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&bull; QUICKLY CONNECT WITH YOUR CONTACTS: Your address book is used to quickly and easily connect you with your contacts who have WhatsApp so there&rsquo;s no need to add hard-to-remember usernames.<br />\n<br />\n&bull; OFFLINE MESSAGES: Even if you miss your notifications or turn off your phone, WhatsApp will save your recent messages until the next time you use the app.<br />\n<br />\n&bull; AND MUCH MORE: Share your location, exchange contacts, set custom wallpapers and notification sounds, email chat history, broadcast messages to multiple contacts at once, and more!</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', 'WhatsApp Inc.', 'November 2, 2015', 119523, 'ON', 'none'),
