(141, 'Opera Mini web browser', 'ios', '30.6M', '11.0.0', '0', 'https://itunes.apple.com/en/app/opera-mini-web-browser/id363729560?mt=8', 'Opera-Mini-Web-Browser.png', '<div class=\"thumbnail\"><span class=\"pre\" style=\"display:none\"></span><span class=\"next\" style=\"display:block\"></span><div class=\"list\" style=\"\"><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/2yI_NSwoZTgo83A2yU57OiNrKZhf4MUfUW8bgGzMUjodJPFY0WvtHqYNQPi1xerWGws=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/h3TWnMOJLRtOvC6-msiBJAGEmqDBF_o8foUKgmmtbKuqdZc2opcEG2F0tVtETPmiJiQ=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-JfhL4SUyNX8uSdRj3OBjdKC1ZlLalvuf0JMRw7S5F0synOaoczM8rTvsWmlWTLqR5WB=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/cQBGxLNPGlh7OSav3lpDasXjRz-JFMwoNxSLokPhMAxQguVx1c-zO-Hz_ABK7c-KUBE=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/vQAP60QT32uQ61pWyNhYPdMQs_Ng9gmgTeSEtSI2ImkwVVlrN7smT1jiGepb_8TZ3DlD=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ykFX7GppsiOFnxJt-KnonlHzsProHFBy60Vuj6i_1ajKSmbY0jTE1i3lSlAPBUJysFvL=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/BurtwP_EZr6H0Lph4EixTpKc10iTKXTPuk_GH7lf1Mcv4UMJiRPG2nZrlRJEwAegMA=h900-rw\" /> <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/DEMHNbbwBLi2_2lomvqK5IjqSr7ov66sPsMu0GyUrfbLsRjFCP-ZeQZo_7GrhFuOSA=h900-rw\" />[END_IMAGE]<h2><strong>What is opera mini web browser?</strong></h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=141\"><strong>Opera Mini</strong></a> lets the user take the Web everywhere with him. The new version is much faster with noticeable speed improvements for all users. This latest version supports <strong>browser </strong>skin personalization and users can also sync their notes now between the <a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\"><strong>android</strong></a> and Opera.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;opera mini web browser app review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/2P_31GMF4Z8?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>âœ” Save your favorite sites: Tap the&nbsp;<strong>+</strong>&nbsp;button on the search bar to save a page to Speed Dial, add it to your mobile bookmarks or read it offline.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>âœ” Get the latest news: Enjoy one-click access to the top stories and freshest content from across the internet.</p>\n\n<p>âœ” Sync your content: Access your favorite bookmarks, Speed Dials or open tabs across all devices.</p>\n\n<p>âœ” Night mode: Dim the screen to reduce eye strain.</p>\n\n<p>âœ” Customize your browser: Tailor <strong>Opera Mini</strong> with different looks to suit your style.</p>\n\n<p>âœ” Switch up your search: Choose between different search engines to suit your needs.</p>\n\n<p>âœ” Manage tabs easily: Opera is designed for ease of use, which means less hassle to get where you want, quickly.</p>\n', 'Opera Software ASA', 'Sep 2, 2015', 88084, 'ON', 'none'),
(142, 'LEO Privacy Guard', 'ios', '19.8M', '1.6', '1', 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/leo-privacy-guard-safe-qr/id1013745810?mt=8', 'LEO Privacy Guard.png', '<[BEGIN_IMAGE]<img src=\"http://a1.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/5e/db/f7/5edbf72c-730f-c2a2-19a3-efc303888362/screen322x572.jpeg\" /> <img src=\"http://a5.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple6/v4/29/d0/3f/29d03ffd-206c-0bd1-aca6-ae0019dafd73/screen322x572.jpeg\" /> <img src=\"http://a5.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple6/v4/b6/c4/a8/b6c4a88b-a53d-d30b-ac71-12335b2ea57c/screen322x572.jpeg\" /> <img src=\"http://a3.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple6/v4/8a/53/a2/8a53a207-8c21-ad2b-8298-58c94ee9d9ce/screen322x572.jpeg\" /> <img src=\"http://a5.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple69/v4/42/71/bd/4271bd2b-840b-2271-f82d-2534fd6d53ad/screen322x572.jpeg\" /> <img src=\"http://a1.mzstatic.com/us/r30/Purple1/v4/4b/c6/a7/4bc6a775-91e3-15d8-091f-4f6784880189/screen322x572.jpeg\">[END_IMAGE]<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2><strong>What is&nbsp;LEO Privacy Guard?</strong></h2>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/index.php?details=142\"><strong>LEO Privacy Guard</strong></a> is the most Trusted and Convenient protector for your personal Photos &amp; Videos!&nbsp;<br />\nKeep your Secrets from annoying snoopers and prying eyes!<br />\nAll the personal images or videos can be safely hidden in <strong>Privacy Guard</strong> by your own Passcode, Pattern or Fingerprints. Then, you will no longer worry about daily &quot;phone check&quot;, accidental access or gossip fingers.</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Video&nbsp;&nbsp;LEO Privacy Guard App Review</strong></h2>\n<center><iframe width=\"480\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/sT_mrM_2jC8?showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>What does LEO Privacy Guard do?</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>AppLock</strong><br />\n- Just a click to lock all apps.<br />\n- Simple switch to change multiple modes.<br />\n- Various ways to cover <strong><a href=\"http://gamemobilez.com/\">your apps</a></strong>, Mask on apps, Guard on phone.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Privacy Protection</strong><br />\n- Privacy alerts keep you informed of phone safety.<br />\n- Keep snoopers away from private pics, videos, SMS and call log.</p>\n\n<p><strong>APP Management</strong><br />\n- Uninstall unwanted apps and back up the important ones.<br />\n- Keep your data plan and battery usage under control easily.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Stunning New Design</strong><br />\n- New design for user interface, simple, handy and intuitive.<br />\n- Stylish themes to decorate your lock screen.</p>\n\n<p><strong>shortcuts</strong><br />\n- Swipe to all APP with shortcuts<br />\n- Everything within reach.</p>\n', 'LEO Network Technology Co., Ltd.', 'Nov 12, 2015', 146058, 'ON', 'none'),
